description:
Baseline scenario (see Fig. 2): 
        Day 1, before the introduction of any public health measures (R0 = 2.38); 
        Day 4, introduction of basic public health recommendations and government school closures (R0 = 1.66); 
        Day 12, policy of limiting screening to symptomatic individuals only (R0 = 1.80);
        Day 22: introduction of incomplete lockdown (R0 = 1.60);
        Day 28: fully operational lockdown with strict measures, working is no longer a good reason for going out: gradually, non-indispensable activities are stopped (R0 = 0.99);
        Day 38: wider testing campaign is launched (R0 = 0.85).
